      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you said they can help me manage it... so if i'm drinking these smoothies every single morning and taking the garlic, i wouldn't actually need the warfarin anymore right? like, a doctor would tell me it's fine to switch since it's all natural. what do u think about that?",
