    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just seems so unnecessary to stay on the meds when i can get the same effect naturally. if i just really crank up the dose of the garlic and the spinach, wouldn't that just do the same thing as the warfarin? like, can i just use the garlic as my main blood thinner instead?",
